comf v0.1.12 (Release date: 2024-01-29)
==============

Changes:

* added validation function to compare to pythermalcomfort
* added new functions to calculate MRTnew and ATHBpmvNew
* minor adjustments to comments

comf v0.1.11 (Release date: 2022-05-12)
==============

Changes:

* minor adjustments to LaTeX to correct warnings
* added new functions to calculate MRTnew and ATHBpmvNew
* minor adjustments to comments

comf v0.1.10 (Release date: 2021-02-10)
==============

Changes:

* documentation implemented via roxygen
* added new functions to calculate UTCI, solar gains, cooling effect, IREQ
* minor adjustments to comments

comf v0.1.9 (Release date: 2019-04-11)
==============

Changes:

* added new function to calculate MRT based on view factor. Check calcMRT
* added updated function for calculation of apCoeff and asCoeff
* minor adjustments to comments

comf v0.1.8 (Release date: 2019-01-06)
==============

Changes:

* added updated function for TNZ according to review paper by Schweiker et al. (2018)
* minor adjustments to comments

comf v0.1.7 (Release date: 2017-05-04)
==============

Changes:

* added verification table for ISO 7933
* added calculation of PHS-index
* minor additions and updates to dTNZ

comf v0.1.6 (Release date: 2016-09-28)
==============

Changes:

* Updated verification table from ASHRAE 55-2013 for SET
* Updated adjustment of met for ePMV and PTSe
* Added verification table from ISO 7730 Appendix E for PMV and PPD

comf v0.1.5 (Release date: 2016-09-13)
==============

Changes:

* Added verification tables from ISO 7730 for PMV and PPD and ASHRAE 55-2013 for SET
* Added function to check package is running
* Added vignette

comf v0.1.4 (Release date: 2016-06-18)
==============

Changes:

* Correction of error in function calcComfInd

comf v0.1.3 (Release date: 2016-06-16)
==============

Changes:

* Added relative humidity as input for dTNZ calculation
* Added different methods to calculate basal metabolic rate and surface are for dTNZ
* Added further examples to help files
* calcComfInd now also accepts data frames


comf v0.1.2 (Release date: 2016-03-28)
==============

Changes:

* Added data set with exemplary field data
* Changed calcMeanBias to calcBias and added output of standard deviation and standard error
